<span class="flex-1 min-w-0 text-base font-medium text-white pr-4 group-hover:text-clarity-blue transition-colors leading-snug">Votre offre est-elle adaptée à mon métier (sophrologue, naturopathe, hypnothérapeute…) ?</span>
<div class="icon-container flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-clarity-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
<svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24">
